build for javascript backend

when user calls POST /api/calculate sending data:
  num_a is data's a
  num_b is data's b
  op is data's operation

  if op is 'add':
    result is num_a + num_b
    send back { result is result }

  if op is 'subtract':
    result is num_a - num_b
    send back { result is result }

  if op is 'multiply':
    result is num_a * num_b
    send back { result is result }

  if op is 'divide':
    if num_b is 0:
      send back { error is 'Division by zero' } with status 400
    result is num_a / num_b
    send back { result is result }
